socialist oil field worker and a singerdancer who used to cavort 
in a green bikini across the street from city hall every day 
the winner of tuesdays mayors race will oversee los angeles at 
least into the early 1990s leading a city with a population that 
is swelling past 3 million people 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
