being held in lebanon two others possibly were dead while 13 were 
released during the year 
ranked behind israel in order as sites for the most terrorist 
incidents were pakistan colombia spain lebanon west germany 
zimbabwe south korea peru and france 
the 10 countries accounted for 75 percent of the incidents 
during the year the report said 
the palestinian uprising which began in december 1987 and 
continued through last year in the israeliheld west bank and gaza 
strip should be viewed overall as a civil insurrection the 
