those payments are not exempt from the house rule limiting outside 
earned income as royalties are 
alexander also alleged that the promotional deal amounted to 
four apparent violations of house limitations on gifts one 
instance of possible conversion of campaign funds to personal use 
two possible instances of conversion of government resources to 
personal use one apparent violation of house financial disclosure 
rules and one apparent violation of the campaign finance law 
