coordination said any proposed development in the chukchi sea 
north of the bering strait likely would be scrutinized carefully 
by the state and federal governments 
virtually anything right now dealing with oil and gas has to 
be taken in context of the valdez disaster grogan said 
theres a tremendous amount of clamor in the lower 48 and 
