as quickly as possible must be balanced with the realization that 
some areas would be better left to a slower cleanup job by nature 
im optimistic that the officials here understand that he 
said i would hope that the public doesnt get frustrated with 
what might seem like a slow process and not press us into doing it 
too fast 
