their fusion process produced four times as much energy as it used 
i dont think the heat they see is due to fusion said 
jones who announced last month he had independently created cold 
nuclear fusion but produced only a miniscule energy release 
physicists said the fleischmannpons experiment might have been 
simply a chemical reaction and therefore not significant as an 
energy source 
