centennial celebration which includes a gallery exhibit and a 
twoweek film retrospective 
in frankfurt germany the old opera house screened the 
circus a 1928 movie about a tramp who takes refuge from the 
police in a circus and a retrospective of his work will be shown 
in munich an international conference will held in paris during 
