the french minister of culture 
a woman of paris which chaplin directed in 1923 will be 
screened with how to make movies an unfinished film he made 
around 1918 at the cinematheque in portugal japanese television 
will have a musical tribute on april 16 
nrkradio in norway will have a 45minute special charlie 
chaplin the clown who chastised and a program consisting of 
his own soundtrack music 
key video will release the charlie chaplin centennial 
