a special show opening april 29 and running through the summer 
will feature photographs documents and other exhibits focusing on 
the 25 years chaplin spent in the vevey region 
festivities will wind up with a chaplin retrospective at the 
annual vevey festival of comic films launched in 1980 in the 
comedians memory organizers plan to screen 51 of chaplins movies 
in a retrospective 
